                <dd>late 8th-early 7th century BCE</dd>
                                        <dt>Places</dt>
                <dd>
                                                            Creation Place: Ancient & Byzantine World, Europe, Thessaly                                                      </dd>
                                        <dt>Period</dt>
                <dd>Geometric period to Orientalizing</dd>
